<abstract>&lt;p&gt;This Just the Facts Series details Administrative Wage Garnishment (AWG). SSA, subject to certain exceptions can use AWG to collect any overpayment that is “past due”. SSA can use AWG while it is also taking other action regarding the overpayment, such as, tax refund interception. This series outline the AWG option.&lt;/p&gt;</abstract>
